<br>
1) It's faster casting than most pull spell options.  (Load the low level bolt if you want more distance distance).<br>
<br>
2) It's so little damage that the pet will have no problems taking aggro on the pull.<br>
<br>
3) It has a mana cost you'll find hard to even see on the bar.<br>
<br>
4) You'll get full exp! <p><img src="http://www.ballio.com/bothsig.gif">
